				<td colspan="2" height="100%" valign="top"><span class="postbody">I can't comment on the other class changes, but the Reincarnation tweak for shamans was HUGE.
<br />

<br />
We don't have any native way to shake hate when we deal too much damage or incur too much from healing...  But it doesn't really matter now.  I can reincarnate with a clean hate rating, and maybe even some extra mana to boot.
<br />

<br />
I'm sure there will be nerf cries soon about it-  I'm already reading stories from PvP land where someone finally manages to kill a shaman and they just pop back up and kill their attackers.</span><br /><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
